item.title: britney part 3
item.description: The Toys-R-Us on state is going out of business so my coworkers and myself are going out of business and all the toys are uber cheap. I picked up a HitClips playerand some britney hitclips. I am excited. It is rather shoddy and it did cost more then it should have(especially considering the brief amusement it caused). I am interested in hacking the little guy.. I would be interested in hooking it up to something else.
